title: Transfer Issues
body: I tried to transfer my account (that was originaly on EUW) from EUNE back to EUW. But now wwhen I try to log in I get this messege: "Your account is in the process of transferring." It has been hours and still no response from the support and I still cant log into my account.

replies.body: It can take a bit for the transfer to process, but if it's been a while do reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).  Our account team can locate any hiccups and help move the transfer along.
